title: Snake Boat Training
comment: The snake boats are traditionally raced through the Kerala backwaters. With 100 rowers and others chanting and beating on the boats hull, its quite a spectacle to see.

title: Secret Beach Path
comment: This path lead round the cliff to a secret beach that was hidden between two cliffs and only accessible by foot.

title: The Red Fort Entrance
comment: The sheer size of this fort was impressive and very hard to get in a single shot.

title: Old Town Delhi
comment: A mad hot pot of people, smells of spices and vibrant colours. Definitely not for the faint hearted!

title: Old Delhi Rooftop View
comment: In the foreground is the minaret of one of the many Mosques throughout Delhi.

title: Zhinan Temple
comment: Placed up in the hills surrounding Taipei, with the fog blowing over, this temple really looked mystical and mysterious.
